\f3\fs27\fsmilli13600 \cb6 KEYID123456
\f0\fs32 \cb3 ). We will need also the\'a0
\f3\fs27\fsmilli13600 \cb6 iss
\f0\fs32 \cb3 \'a0value, this is the Team Id, that can be checked on your Apple's Developer account, in our case it will be\'a0
\f3\fs27\fsmilli13600 \cb6 THEATEAM
