\f0\fs32 \cb3 \'a0variable on the\'a0
\f3\fs27\fsmilli13600 \cb6 config
\f0\fs32 \cb3 \'a0file. By default it is set to 10 (seconds).\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl360\partightenfactor0

